spec_data.Name: ghc-cmark
spec_data.Description:
This package provides Haskell bindings for <https://github.com/jgm/cmark
libcmark>, the reference parser for <http://commonmark.org CommonMark>, a fully
specified variant of Markdown.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 11:15:46 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Fast, accurate CommonMark (Markdown) parser and renderer
